    <title>英语语法</title>
    <link href="/2024/11/07/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/"/>
    <url>/2024/11/07/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="英语语法"><a href="#英语语法" class="headerlink" title="英语语法"></a>英语语法</h2><h3 id="一、基本句型"><a href="#一、基本句型" class="headerlink" title="一、基本句型"></a>一、基本句型</h3><ul><li><p>五种简单的基本句型</p><ul><li><p>主语+谓语</p></li><li><p>主语+谓语+宾语</p></li><li><p>主语+连系动词+表语</p></li><li><p>主语+谓语+间接宾语+直接宾语</p></li><li><p>主语+谓语+宾语+宾语补足语</p></li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="1、”主-谓”和”主-谓-宾”"><a href="#1、”主-谓”和”主-谓-宾”" class="headerlink" title="1、”主+谓”和”主+谓+宾”"></a>1、”主+谓”和”主+谓+宾”</h4><blockquote><ol><li><p>My father works hard.</p></li><li><p>My father likes football.</p></li></ol></blockquote><h4 id="2、”主-系-表”"><a href="#2、”主-系-表”" class="headerlink" title="2、”主+系+表”"></a>2、”主+系+表”</h4><blockquote><ol><li>My father is a teacher.</li><li>My father is humorous.</li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><p>[!Tip]</p><p>不必翻译的动词：be动词</p><p>My father <code>is</code> humorous. 我的爸爸很幽默。</p></blockquote><h5 id="连系动词"><a href="#连系动词" class="headerlink" title="连系动词"></a>连系动词</h5><ol><li>表示特征或状态</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>连系动词</th><th>例句</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>be</td><td>My father is humorous.</td></tr><tr><td>feel</td><td>The metal felt smooth and cold.</td></tr><tr><td>look</td><td>You look tired.</td></tr><tr><td>sound</td><td>That sounds a good idea.</td></tr><tr><td>taste</td><td>The drug tastes bitter.(这药真苦啊！)</td></tr><tr><td>smell</td><td>The cream smells funny.(奶油闻起来好奇怪)</td></tr><tr><td>seem</td><td>She seems nice.</td></tr><tr><td>appear</td><td>His explanation appears unlikely.(他的解释显得很假)</td></tr></tbody></table><ol start="2"><li>表示状态转变</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>连系动词</th><th>例句</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>become</td><td>My father became a teacher ten years ago.</td></tr><tr><td>turn</td><td>My father’s hair is turning grey.</td></tr></tbody></table><ol start="3"><li>表示状态保持</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>连系动词</th><th>例句</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>prove</td><td>English proved easy.</td></tr><tr><td>remain</td><td>We remained friends.</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    
